OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780038278
OL,3,CPeople evacuated from homes after fire
OL,4,Ccaused by lightning strike
OL,6,FA house in Melton Mowbray caught fire
OL,7,Fovernight after being hit by a
OL,8,Flightning strike as the heatwave eased
OL,9,Fgiving way to rain and thunderstorms.
OL,11,FLeicestershire Fire and Rescue Service
OL,12,Fsaid crews were called just before 5am
OL,13,Fto a fire on the roof of a house in
OL,14,FBayswater Road, Melton, after reports
OL,15,Fthat it had been hit during the
OL,16,Fthunderstorm.
OL,18,FThe residents of neighbouring houses
OL,19,Fwere evacuated as a precaution.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
