OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780038278
OL,3,CPeople evacuated from homes after fire
OL,4,Ccaused by lightning strike
OL,6,FAn eye witness described being woken
OL,7,Fup terrified after a huge noise, and
OL,8,Fhearing screams down the street.
OL,10,FShe said she was crying as she and her
OL,11,Ffamily were evacuated from their home.
OL,12,FThey were allowed back in at 9am.
OL,14,FToday a gaping hole could be seen in
OL,15,Fthe roof, with roof tiles and glass on
OL,16,Fthe floor and the front of the house
OL,17,Fwas taped off.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
