CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780038278
OL,3,CPeople evacuated from homes after fire
OL,4,Ccaused by lightning strike
OL,6,FCrews were called in from Melton
OL,7,FMowbray, Oakham, Billesdon and Central
OL,8,FFire Station, with support from fire
OL,9,Fservices in Northamptonshire and
OL,10,FLincolnshire to fight the blaze during
OL,11,Fthe storm.
OL,13,FIn Witherley, fire crews were called
OL,14,Fto a bungalow fire at 3:45 this
OL,15,Fmorning, again, following a direct
OL,16,Flightning strike.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
