OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780038278
OL,3,CPeople evacuated from homes after fire
OL,4,Ccaused by lightning strike
OL,6,FBy the time they arrived, everyone had
OL,7,Fmanaged to leave the building but due
OL,8,Fto intensity of the flames bursting
OL,9,Fthrough the roof, crews had to draw
OL,10,Fback and move to target the
OL,11,Fneighbouring property, where they
OL,12,Fmanaged to stop it from spreading.
OL,14,FRemarkable footage was captured
OL,15,Fovernight across the region as
OL,16,Flightning illuminated the night skies.
OL,18,FPictures from Neil Pugh
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
